{"tid":123874,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"拜金港女Seasun 住過趙世曾豪宅","createTime":"2017-02-17T06:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T09:26:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88d757b254a5f378bfd384172766f1a1d40d8bb1","tid":123874,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:55:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20170217/19930473\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fentertainment%2Fart%2F20170217%2F19930473&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=e28d5036\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fentertainment%2Fart%2F20170217%2F19930473&h=6fd9042c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20170217/19930473</a><br />\n<br />\n拜金港女Seasun<br />\n住過趙世曾豪宅<br />\n<br />\n21,057<br />\nInitial ImagePlay Button Image<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n ■Seasun直認曾入住趙世曾的趙苑。資料圖片<br />\n■Seasun直認曾入住趙世曾的趙苑。資料圖片<br />\n昨日有爆料指拜金港女Seasun當日無家可歸，趙世曾安排她入住「趙苑」，但她突然帶男人返趙苑，最後被趙世曾趕走。昨日本報向Seasun求證，她坦承曾入住趙苑：「嗰時工作我要接待嘉賓，又唔係同佢一齊住，都係盡地主之誼，趙生好gentleman。」問她是否帶男人入趙苑故被趕？她支吾以對，最後又說沒有。<br />\n節目未出街，她已被圍插，Seasun回應：「有啲係我自己（講），有啲可能係效果剪接。」問她為何會講「有樓有高潮」？她稱：「我嗰句係有個安穩嘅住屋條件，喺個舒服啲嘅地方，容易啲達到高潮。」至於「冇樓唔好白撞」呢？她說：「佢嗰時問我擇偶條件，跟住我提到其中一樣嘢係有樓，如果唔係以上咁多條件唔好白撞。」<br />\n<br />\n ■拜金港女Seasun（右）前日和張秀文宣傳，Seasun因言論出位被圍插。<br />\n■拜金港女Seasun（右）前日和張秀文宣傳，Seasun因言論出位被圍插。<br />\n趙世曾：畀地方佢住<br />\n本報向趙世曾求證Seasun曾幫他打工，更獲安排入住趙苑一事，他表示沒印象：「趙苑成日都裝修，都會有安排宿舍畀員工，有時會安排馬來西亞、內地員工嚟，係會畀地方佢哋住，但你哋講個女仔就冇印象。」<br />\n對於節目《有樓萬事足》被外界質疑有劇本，節目編導岑應回應傳媒時表示：「冇事先安排劇本，第一次同呢個女仔（Seasun）傾電話，已經覺得佢嘅思維好得意，其他我唔方便答，你哋問番公司啦！」<br />\n採訪：嵐山  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n現職公關曾選美「有樓有高潮」素人大起底"},{"pid":"245bb5f16a4bf64087b4dd4fdeca5000f27444f4","tid":123874,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20170217/org/1487271841_a310.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170217%2Forg%2F1487271841_a310.jpg&h=22bccdf2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb0d6237b61326bd957f0459e77f4bb4ce483925","tid":123874,"uid":77084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20170217/org/1487271841_a310.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170217%2Forg%2F1487271841_a310.jpg&h=22bccdf2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n下巴咩事"},{"pid":"e081cbb9599664002a55aa67e16b632b8fbea834","tid":123874,"uid":64356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zrkn7wfc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzrkn7wfc&h=45828c71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9853f6fd9da544d5298041ce64c39fad8bc5c712","tid":123874,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:24:38.000Z","msg":"雞即係雞。 你根本唔識做人"},{"pid":"c56d13670c8072c7d1fb44c988b99cb34361e682","tid":123874,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:26:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}